description:
A command-line Baidu Netdisk client that emulates Linux Shell file manipulation commands, based on the original version of iikira/BaiduPCS-Go with additional ability of saving shared files

A command-line Baidu Netdisk client written in Go, providing useful functionalities for operating Baidu Netdisk.
This version is based on iikira's original BaiduPCS-Go v3.6.2, with additional ability of saving shared files.
